data.title: Bayfront MRT station
authors: Contributors to Marina Bay : Reimagined Wiki
data.meta_description: Bayfront MRT station is an underground Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) station on the Downtown line, located in Downtown Core, Singapore underneath Bayfront Avenue between the junctions of Bayfront Link and Sheares Link. Bayfront station primarily serves the integrated resort of Marina Bay Sands.
data.text:
Bayfront MRT station is an underground Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) station on the Downtown line, located in Downtown Core, Singapore underneath Bayfront Avenue between the junctions of Bayfront Link and Sheares Link.

Bayfront station primarily serves the integrated resort of Marina Bay Sands.
